    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "a0mThGuide",
      "x": -450,
      "y": 0,
      "name": "00 · 深浅色切换说明",
      "width": 400,
      "height": 300,
      "fill": "$theme.surface",
      "cornerRadius": 16,
      "stroke": {
        "align": "inside",
        "thickness": 1,
        "fill": "$theme.border"
      },
      "layout": "vertical",
      "gap": 14,
      "padding": 24,
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "a0mThGT",
          "fill": "$theme.textPrimary",
          "content": "深浅色切换入口",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 20,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "a0mThGS",
          "fill": "$theme.textSecondary",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 352,
          "content": "Pencil 没有应用内的「一键换肤」按钮。请打开 Variables（变量）面板（工具栏中的变量/调色板类图标，或侧边栏），在变量表顶部的 Mode 列里，在 light 与 dark 之间切换即可预览整套配色；布尔变量 dark_mode 会随当前 Mode 分别解析为 false / true。",
          "lineHeight": 1.45,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "a0mThGH",
          "fill": "$theme.tertiary",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 352,
          "content": "若看不到 Mode 列：请在变量表中启用主题轴「mode」（或新建集合并勾选 light / dark 两列）。",
          "lineHeight": 1.4,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        }
      ]
    },
